January 8, 2026, read first time and referred to Committee on Local Government.
January 20, 2026, amended, reported — Do Pass.
January 22, 2026, read second time, amended, ordered engrossed.
January 23, 2026, engrossed.
January 27, 2026, read third time, passed. Yeas 76, nays 15.
