35 and
36 (3) complies with or is otherwise exempt from any applicable
37 building codes, fire safety codes, and other public health and
38 safety laws.
39 The term does not include a manufactured home (as defined in
40 IC 36-7-4-1106(b)) that is subject to the standards and
41 requirements set forth in IC 36-7-4-1106.
