(4) The percentage of new residential dwelling units
constructed that are listed at each of the following:
(A) Eighty percent (80%) or less of the unit's median
income.
(B) Eighty-one percent (81%) to one hundred nineteen
percent (119%) of the unit's median income.
(C) One hundred twenty percent (120%) or more of the
