requirement.
(c) A unit shall use applicable data and information from the
2025 calendar year as a reference point for the information
required to be reported under subsection (b).
(d) The authority must compile and publish on the authority's
website an annual report of the information reported by units
under subsection (b) that includes at least the following:
(1) Regional comparisons of the information provided under
subsection (b).
(2) An evaluation of the outcomes of housing legislation
enacted during the 2026 legislative session.".
